Body: Description: Reference ticket 00424345...working with previous engineer who assisted with setting up multiple seek jobs with different hosts.  The issue now is that when i configure v2 scan with the noted hosts if replicates to scan_v3 & scan_v4 respectively. even if i switch and configure scan_v3 with a different host it will sync to the other 2 scans that previous engineer walked me thru.

Hi @Dusty Grayson​,

 

Thanks for flagging this ticket for a KB. Would you clarify some details?

 

  1. Can you explain more about the Symptom? Could you show it in a screenshot or demonstrate in some other way what is happening?
  2. Do we know anything else about the Cause such as this issue occurring after an upgrade, moving jobs around, etc.?

 

CC: @Jake Mahon​ @Nicholas Zimmer​

What We've Learned Updated: Cause:
Unknown, suspect that the .xml files with the copied job would not correctly update thus making the console display the last edited host.
